## Key Sections Covered

- **Business Value & ROI:** Understanding the why behind the feature
- **Target Users:** Who will benefit and how they'll use it
- **Success Criteria:** How to measure feature success
- **Implementation Approach:** High-level technical strategy
- **Timeline & Resources:** Planning and estimation
- **Risk Assessment:** Potential challenges and mitigation

## Audience Focus

**Primary Audience:** Product managers, business stakeholders, feature owners
**Secondary Audience:** Development teams, designers, project managers

